data.title: 准备以至少30秒的时间回答以下问题
data.answer: There are two little girls standing side by side, and they both wear colorful dresses, one of them is wearing a green dress and a pink hat, the other one wears a purple dress and a green hat. They both wearing sunglasses to protect their eyes from the severe sunshine during summer. On their left-hand side, there is a huge tree trunk, and it seems that there is a snake beside the tree. One of the little girls is looking at it, while the other one is smiling at the camera. Although the snake may be non-toxic, these two girls are still very brave. （103 字）
